## 3. Services Layer

### 3a. `services/index.ts`
- `getCollectorQuadrants(token, clientId, params)` → `GET /v2/clients/${clientId}/managements/collector-quadrants` — paginated, filterable by quadrant + search
- `getManagementIndicators(token, clientId)` → `GET /v2/clients/${clientId}/managements/indicators` — status, tasks, payment commitments, daily/monthly goals, overdue reduction

### 3b. `services/tracks.ts`
- `createTrack(token, clientId, payload)` → `POST /v2/clients/${clientId}/managements/tracks` — creates single track, returns track + phaseTransitions
- `createMultipleTracks(token, clientId, payloads)` → sequential `createTrack` calls, collects errors
- `getDebtorTracks(token, clientId, debtorId, params)` → `GET /v2/clients/${clientId}/managements/tracks/debtor/${debtorId}` — paginated, filterable by status/type/result/executive/date
- `getDebtorTracksByInvoices(token, clientId, debtorId, params)` → `GET .../debtor/${debtorId}/invoices` — tracks grouped by invoices
- `getTrackById(token, clientId, trackId)` → `GET /v2/clients/${clientId}/managements/tracks/${trackId}`

### 3c. `services/sip.ts`
- `getSipCallExternalId(token, clientId)` → `GET /bff/api/v2/clients/${clientId}/sip-call-external-id` — returns PBX uniqueid for call tracking

### 3d. `services/payment-plan.ts`
- `createPaymentPlan({ token, clientId, dataToInsert })` → `POST /v2/clients/${clientId}/payment-plans` — calculates installment via amortization formula, computes end date, sends full plan payload
- Helper functions: `getFrequencyFactor()`, `calculateInstallmentAmount()`, `calculateEndDate()`, `formatToISO()`

### 3e. `services/email-builder.ts`
- `buildEmailPayload({ managementFormData, selectedInvoices, profile, managementCombination, bankAccountInfo })` → constructs `EmailPayload` for single management email
- Formats invoices, calculates total amount, generates body description via `generateBodyDescriptionByDebtorComment()`, replaces placeholders ({amount}, {date}, {email_company}, {bank_account_info}, {name_client})

### 3f. `services/email-builder-multiple.ts`
- `buildMultipleEmailPayload({ managements, profile, contactEmail, contactName, bankAccountInfo })` → constructs `EmailMultiplePayload` for multiple managements in one email
- Groups managements, formats each independently, uses generic body description

### 3g. `services/email-sender.ts`
- `sendTrackEmail(payload, token, clientId)` → `POST /v2/clients/${clientId}/managements/emails/send` — 10s timeout
- `sendMultipleManagementEmail(payload, token, clientId)` → same endpoint, 15s timeout

### 3h. `services/bank-info-formatter.ts`
- `fetchAndFormatBankInfo(token, clientId, clientName, clientEmail)` → fetches bank info from `getAllBankInformations()`, returns formatted object
- `generateBankInfoHTML(bankInfo)` → HTML block with bank entity, account number, type, holder, email
- `generateBankInfoText(bankInfo)` → plain text version

