## Architecture Summary

```
Parent Route: /dashboard/debtor-management
├── IndicatorsDebtor (sidebar metrics)
├── TaskFilters (quadrant filter + search + export)
│   └── DebtorSearchAutocomplete
└── TasksList
    └── TaskIsland × 6 quadrants
        └── TaskItem (click → detail page)

Detail Route: /dashboard/debtor-management/[id]
├── DebtorContacts (VoIP calling)
└── Tabs
    ├── KeyReasonsTab
    │   ├── DebtorChatbot (AI assistant)
    │   └── Collapsible cards:
    │       ├── KeyReasons
    │       ├── PaymentCommitment
    │       ├── CreditRisk
    │       ├── ProtestedChecks
    │       ├── LastPaymentReceived
    │       ├── LitigationsCard
    │       └── LastManagements → managements-list
    └── AddManagementTab (3-step wizard)
        ├── Step 1: Invoice selection
        ├── Step 2: Management type cascade + dynamic fields
        │   ├── ManagementLitigationForm
        │   ├── ManagementNormalizedLitigationForm
        │   └── ManagementPaymentPlanForm
        └── Step 3: Preview + file upload + email checkbox
        On finish → createTrack + optionally createLitigation/createPaymentPlan + sendEmail

Managements List Route: /dashboard/debtor-management/[id]/managements-list
├── Debtor info header
├── DataTableDynamicColumns (20 configurable columns)
│   └── InvoiceWithTrack data
└── TrackDetailModal (full management detail)

Root Managements List: /dashboard/debtor-management/managements-list
