```

### Data Flow:
1. Debtor data from `useDebtorsStore` (Zustand)
2. Collection profile + call brief from store
3. Collector quadrants from React Query (`useCollectorQuadrants`)
4. Management indicators from React Query (`useManagementIndicators`)
5. WebRTC call state from `WebRTCContext` + `useWebRTCPhone`
6. Chat thread persistence in `useDebtorsStore`
7. Profile/session from `ProfileContext`

### Key API Endpoints:
- `GET /v2/clients/{id}/managements/collector-quadrants`
- `GET /v2/clients/{id}/managements/indicators`
- `POST /v2/clients/{id}/managements/tracks`
- `GET /v2/clients/{id}/managements/tracks/debtor/{debtorId}`
- `GET /v2/clients/{id}/managements/tracks/debtor/{debtorId}/invoices`
- `GET /v2/clients/{id}/managements/tracks/{trackId}`
- `POST /v2/clients/{id}/managements/emails/send`
- `POST /v2/clients/{id}/payment-plans`
- `GET /bff/api/v2/clients/{id}/sip-call-external-id`
- `POST /v2/clients/{id}/ai-engines/chat`
